= Installation

1. Copy plugin to <radiant>/vendor/extensions/file_browser/

2. Create web server write-able 'assets' folder in 'public' (<radiant>/vendor/public/assets)

3. Migrate extensions

   (from root of application)
   % rake radiant:extensions:file_browser:migrate RAILS_ENV="production"

4. Run the extension update task.
 
   (from root of application)
   % rake radiant:extensions:file_browser:update

5. Restart web server

If installed correctly, "File Browser" will be listed on extensions listing (http://locahost:3000/admin/extensions)
